Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OP
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.18,0:01:22.54,OP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}私の生まれた　この場所この部屋で
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.42,0:01:25.61,OP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}出会ったよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.31,0:01:33.09,OP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}照ぼけたランプは　いまも優しい光を
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.24,0:01:37.21,OP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}照らしてくれる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.80,0:01:43.20,OP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}ずっと昔から　紡がれてきた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.26,0:01:48.40,OP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}時間をきつかせてくれた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.51,0:01:54.46,OP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}胸にとまそう　心の中のランプ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.56,0:01:59.22,OP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}今隠れてた絆照らし
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.30,0:02:05.21,OP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}私にそっと　囁きかけるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.30,0:02:09.85,OP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}ああ　僕らいつもここだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.02,0:02:12.36,OP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}差し伸べた手　ほら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.46,0:02:17.25,OP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}繋いたら　君に言おう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.35,0:02:22.85,OP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}言葉は　意味を信じているから
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.94,0:02:28.21,OP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}この手を放さないでいて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.18,0:01:22.54,OP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}在我出生的 這個地方這間房屋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.42,0:01:25.61,OP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}與你邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.31,0:01:33.09,OP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}照耀昏暗的油燈 如今也依舊用那溫暖的微光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.24,0:01:37.21,OP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}把我的心靈照亮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.80,0:01:43.20,OP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}從很久以前 故事就在悄然編織
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.26,0:01:48.40,OP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}讓我察覺到了光陰的流逝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.51,0:01:54.46,OP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}請停留在我胸膛裏 那心靈的明燈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.56,0:01:59.22,OP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}如今也照亮那深藏的羈絆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.30,0:02:05.21,OP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}請悄悄於我耳畔細語
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.30,0:02:09.85,OP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}啊啊 我們一直都未曾離開
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.02,0:02:12.36,OP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}伸展出雙臂 看那
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.46,0:02:17.25,OP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}如果能夠觸碰到你 就把這一切向你訴說
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.35,0:02:22.85,OP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}正如字裏行間所傳達的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.94,0:02:28.21,OP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}請不要放開我的手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-----------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.01,0:00:19.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宮司先生也不容易啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.90,0:00:23.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真琴才4歲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.80,0:00:25.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是特別需要寵愛的時期呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.39,0:00:43.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是叫真琴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.16,0:00:46.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看得見我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.27,0:00:53.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你就是15代繼承人了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.20,0:00:59.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那便是我和銀太郎的初次相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.92,0:02:46.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(460,370)\pos(613,385)\3c&H000000&\shad0\bord2\be3}「15代繼承人和銀太郎」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.09,0:02:54.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我家雖然不大
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.90,0:02:57.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但也是從江戶時代一直延傳下來的稻荷神社
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.62,0:03:04.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裏供奉的是象徵富饒的宇迦之御魂大神
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.62,0:03:04.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs21}宇迦之御魂大神：日本神話中的稻禾大神，死後留下五穀，它同時也是狐神。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.14,0:03:13.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 怎麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.15,0:03:15.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.98,0:03:19.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裏居住著 宮司的爸爸和女兒的我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.67,0:03:24.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及神明大人的使者 神使銀太郎我們三人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.23,0:03:29.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 真琴 大清早的吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.37,0:03:32.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 銀太郎 早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.41,0:03:35.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,銀太郎大人在屋頂上嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.43,0:03:35.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.00,0:03:40.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遺憾的是 身為這家女婿的爸爸我看不見啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.62,0:03:46.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今後也拜託您照顧我家真琴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.50,0:03:49.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為銀太郎是神使
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.17,0:03:51.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以一般人是看不見的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.75,0:03:56.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我之所以能看見是因為我是這裏的正統繼承人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.39,0:03:59.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來 真琴 上學還來得及嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.79,0:04:01.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 爸爸 這個給你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.29,0:04:03.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.67,0:04:04.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢走
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.94,0:04:08.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一般來說神使都是成對的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.48,0:04:13.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另外一個好像在百年前離開了這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.56,0:04:17.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如今我家的神使就只有銀太郎一人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.78,0:04:20.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是神社最關鍵的是信仰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.87,0:04:22.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神明保佑還是不變的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.34,0:04:30.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 我要乘車
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.71,0:04:39.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 治癒魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.57,0:04:41.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣就能快快好起來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.90,0:04:42.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.46,0:04:45.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是真琴姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.12,0:04:49.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.17,0:04:52.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小幸 小秋 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.72,0:04:55.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貓咪怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.50,0:04:59.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受傷了 大家決定在傷好之前照顧它
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.23,0:05:00.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它叫小咪哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.12,0:05:03.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快點好起來就好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.76,0:05:04.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.69,0:05:05.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.55,0:05:09.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐來不及了 再見啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.06,0:05:10.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜拜 明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.90,0:05:13.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐又要遲到了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.45,0:05:23.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,起立 敬禮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.40,0:05:27.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冱木 等會來辦公室一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.28,0:05:28.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,out
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.80,0:05:34.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.23,0:05:38.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新學期剛開始就…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.10,0:05:39.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冱木
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.41,0:05:41.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.19,0:05:43.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是由美 池上由美
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.52,0:05:45.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有點話要和你說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.57,0:05:47.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.67,0:05:50.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說你很擅長占卜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.23,0:05:55.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,銀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.51,0:05:59.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,銀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.00,0:06:02.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在哪裏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.07,0:06:07.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,銀 銀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.67,0:06:08.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.20,0:06:13.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,銀太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.96,0:06:16.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰會待在那種地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.44,0:06:20.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了 班裏有同學想要我給她占卜下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.30,0:06:24.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你把神使當作什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.83,0:06:26.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給你橘子吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.75,0:06:55.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別人再怎麼看不見你也別…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.15,0:06:59.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和男朋友吵架了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.93,0:07:21.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.17,0:07:25.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 沒什麼大問題
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.36,0:07:26.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.22,0:07:29.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 對方好像也很想道歉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.50,0:07:35.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是小心點哦 這女孩性格非常要強啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.16,0:07:38.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說到底還是要放低架子 以謙虛的態度…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.79,0:07:40.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.21,0:07:41.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了呢 由美
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.63,0:07:44.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看 和她商量下果然是正確的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.23,0:07:45.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs31}請盡量謙虛點…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.81,0:07:48.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見啦 冱木 謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.66,0:07:51.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謙虛 謙虛點呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.22,0:07:56.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 如此胡亂使喚狐神的神官主還是第一次遇到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.50,0:08:00.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夕子可比你賢淑 有女人味多了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.32,0:08:03.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別拿我和媽媽比呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.90,0:08:08.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之 我可再也不做了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.25,0:08:09.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使有橘子也不
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.22,0:08:12.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.84,0:08:14.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來 再給我一個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.01,0:08:16.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.20,0:08:28.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來為什麼喜歡橘子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.39,0:08:35.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,池上同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.93,0:08:43.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,招搖撞騙 說什麼我去道歉就能和好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.13,0:08:46.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是按你說的和他道歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.94,0:08:49.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明我都開口向他道歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.67,0:08:55.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.57,0:08:58.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才來占卜的同學
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.74,0:09:00.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,據說關係更加惡化了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.82,0:09:02.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是說了沒問題的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.81,0:09:05.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 關我什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.36,0:09:08.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說到底也就是占卜罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.57,0:09:09.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.97,0:09:13.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為銀的占卜是特別的 所以大家才都依賴你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.64,0:09:15.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,依賴我的是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.75,0:09:21.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說到底 你沒把我說的話好好傳達給那女孩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.60,0:09:26.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.20,0:09:29.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 一個二個都這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.87,0:09:32.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平常都不來神社參拜的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.50,0:09:34.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唯獨困擾時才來祈求神靈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.33,0:09:38.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,饒了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.50,0:09:41.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼不可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.74,0:09:43.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們家是神社
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.24,0:09:45.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人們困擾時依賴我們有什麼不對
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.30,0:09:49.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 說到占卜的話 夕子可比你要…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.80,0:09:53.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,銀不也是 說什麼是神明的使者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.73,0:09:55.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不就是個普通的狐貍嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.02,0:10:01.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.86,0:10:04.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正我就是個喜歡惡作劇的臭狐貍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.23,0:10:09.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們都被我耍得團團轉呢 活該
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.20,0:10:12.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.57,0:10:15.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,銀你個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.75,0:10:20.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最討厭你了 快走開
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.75,0:10:25.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎 我不在的話困擾的可是你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.05,0:10:28.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行了 我才不管
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.60,0:11:14.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真琴姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.56,0:11:18.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦啊 小咪它
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.90,0:11:20.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.63,0:11:22.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小咪是指昨天公園裏的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.86,0:11:26.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被車子撞的傷明明眼看就要痊癒了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.50,0:11:30.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了 真琴姐姐的話一定能夠找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.80,0:11:33.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上次就幫我找到了媽媽的戒指
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.00,0:11:36.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 那個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.20,0:11:40.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.60,0:11:43.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒問題的 我和你們一起找
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.40,0:11:45.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告訴我一些小咪可能會去的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.50,0:11:46.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.22,0:11:50.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 髒死了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.60,0:11:55.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個小祠堂 難道不在稻荷大神老爺子的管轄內嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.97,0:12:00.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前明明稻荷的領土都是隨處可見的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.35,0:12:05.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這一帶也真是變了不少啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.90,0:12:10.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 愛貓的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.02,0:12:13.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小幸 小秋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.32,0:12:15.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.57,0:12:16.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到小咪了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.80,0:12:19.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啊 哪都找不到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.33,0:12:23.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 冱木
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.74,0:12:24.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,池上同學
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.77,0:12:27.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐你們是朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.92,0:12:31.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這位大姐姐帶小咪去的醫院
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.53,0:12:37.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是沒辦法嗎 看到受傷的野貓怎麼忍心放任不管
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.86,0:12:42.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起這個 趕緊找小咪了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.18,0:12:45.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冱木也別在那傻站著
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.70,0:12:54.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,約翰 你怎麼了 亂叫什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.08,0:12:57.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.26,0:13:07.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 不閃其實也沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.00,0:13:10.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說這附近…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.50,0:13:13.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和神官主吵架了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.79,0:13:15.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還算不上神官主呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.11,0:13:20.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神使被人類擺佈這是什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.27,0:13:25.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果沒有祭神之主的話 我們神使是無法存活的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.27,0:13:25.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs21\an7}祭神：此指神使所侍奉的神
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.71,0:13:27.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神社亦是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.61,0:13:30.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有神使的神社就不會有祭神光顧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.94,0:13:32.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然不久便會衰敗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.80,0:13:36.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也快點回你原來的神社吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.52,0:13:38.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打擾了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.01,0:13:45.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來 你的拍檔哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.16,0:13:49.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神使都是合二為一的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.40,0:13:55.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很久前 就沒有了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.46,0:14:00.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到的就只有這個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.71,0:14:03.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它受傷了 應該跑不遠
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.12,0:14:05.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是小咪手上的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.93,0:14:09.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我和小幸一起一邊想著快好起來一邊畫的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.80,0:14:13.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真琴姐姐 請用占卜把小咪找回來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.03,0:14:15.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.08,0:14:21.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,占卜…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.41,0:14:22.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行的 不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.89,0:14:25.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這孩子的占卜根本就算不中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.60,0:14:26.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是之前…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.23,0:14:29.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我打電話問問衛生所看看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.46,0:14:32.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.49,0:14:34.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小咪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.40,0:14:36.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上就幫你們找回來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.73,0:14:40.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,銀你個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.84,0:14:43.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最討厭你了 快走開
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.18,0:14:51.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起呀 是姐姐不好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.57,0:14:52.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍等我一會
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.67,0:14:50.26,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,是的是的 我不是說了很多次了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.57,0:14:54.65,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微有點胖 腿部帶著傷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.21,0:14:55.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.42,0:14:56.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冱木
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.50,0:15:04.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說到底這裏的主人是我才對
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.46,0:15:07.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,管她真琴生不生氣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.01,0:15:09.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,銀太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.00,0:15:13.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,銀太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.82,0:15:17.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,銀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.75,0:15:22.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在哪 銀太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.60,0:15:24.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求你了 快出來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.46,0:15:26.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,銀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.93,0:15:28.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,銀 快出來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.24,0:15:31.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.43,0:15:35.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸 你知道銀太郎去哪了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.09,0:15:39.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸我看不見啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.54,0:15:42.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不在了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.66,0:15:51.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸 怎麼辦啊 銀不在的話就找不到小咪了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.14,0:15:52.45,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 先冷靜下來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.60,0:15:54.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊 又想找我占卜嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.65,0:15:58.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用擔心 肯定不久便會回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.00,0:16:00.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是散步去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.55,0:16:05.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我昨天和銀太郎吵架 說了很過分的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.56,0:16:08.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說什麼「最討厭 快走開」之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.17,0:16:11.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,占卜沒有說中明明是我的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.87,0:16:15.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還說了銀太郎什麼的不就是普通的狐貍嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.28,0:16:21.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要向他道歉的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.14,0:16:25.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 銀太郎他不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.54,0:16:28.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直以來都任著我性子來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.95,0:16:30.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被我折騰 使他困擾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.85,0:16:33.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明有那麼多需要銀的人們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.50,0:16:35.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我卻連這一點都沒有察覺到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.45,0:16:43.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫非只是我奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.74,0:16:45.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,銀從一開始就不存在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.83,0:16:48.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 如果連真琴都這麼說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.10,0:16:51.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼銀太郎大人就真的會不見了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.70,0:17:00.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真琴 你有想過為什麼只有你能看見銀太郎大人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.38,0:17:03.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.35,0:17:06.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸認為
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.10,0:17:13.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真琴請求銀太郎大人占卜絕不是件壞事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.14,0:17:21.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的使命一定就是作為銀太郎大人與人類之間溝通的橋樑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.86,0:17:24.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,溝通的橋樑？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.07,0:17:29.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能親眼看見神使銀太郎大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.30,0:17:32.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能夠彼此傳達語言
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.16,0:17:36.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請你不要忘了這之中的含義
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.77,0:17:39.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,假正經了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.56,0:17:46.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸 我去尋找銀太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.63,0:17:48.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天的事也好好道個歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.64,0:17:50.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後 然後
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.86,0:17:53.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為 有孩子正在等著銀呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.10,0:17:56.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有我才可以找尋到銀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.30,0:17:58.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別太晚哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.03,0:18:03.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 爸爸 多準備些橘子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.92,0:18:08.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 是啊 銀太郎大人的最愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.90,0:18:12.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,銀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.66,0:18:14.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 銀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.77,0:18:18.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明從小就和你在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.84,0:18:21.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 也許就是因為總是在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.17,0:18:25.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我忘掉了銀太郎是神明大人使者的這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.95,0:18:29.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以再次見到銀太郎時 我要好好道歉才行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.41,0:18:31.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,銀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.81,0:18:33.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在哪裏 銀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.16,0:18:35.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,銀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.17,0:18:41.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 你跑哪裏找啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.47,0:18:43.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毛手毛腳的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.81,0:18:51.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,砸死你這只糟蹋莊稼的臭狐貍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.04,0:18:53.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可別再讓我看到你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.50,0:19:01.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.73,0:19:08.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我現在只有橘子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.65,0:19:11.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不介意的話 請吃了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.98,0:19:29.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 混蛋 什麼跟什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.16,0:19:36.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,銀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.13,0:19:39.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,銀太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.54,0:19:45.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.78,0:19:53.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 不是說過誰會待在那種地方了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.29,0:19:55.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,銀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.78,0:19:57.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是銀太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.30,0:19:59.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.41,0:20:02.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,終於找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.47,0:20:04.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.33,0:20:08.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可擔心你了 笨蛋銀太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.75,0:20:13.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 不對
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.50,0:20:17.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 昨天對不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.18,0:20:20.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 怎麼辦啊 銀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.43,0:20:21.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貓咪它
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.48,0:20:22.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小咪它
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.27,0:20:28.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真沒辦法啊 你沒了我什麼都辦不成
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.35,0:20:32.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我吃橘子吃到飽哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.10,0:21:02.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小幸和小秋都很高興哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.06,0:21:05.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 嚇了我一跳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.71,0:21:09.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,池上同學的男朋友把小咪找了回來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.72,0:21:11.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說繃帶脫掉了 還受著傷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.33,0:21:13.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以不忍放著不管
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.13,0:21:18.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,池上同學也誤打誤撞好像和男友和好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.86,0:21:26.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後 那個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.68,0:21:30.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你 銀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.60,0:21:35.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笑什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.87,0:21:41.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我雖然已做了幾百年稻荷大神的使者
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.07,0:21:45.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直以來神官主都是敬畏 崇拜 奉承我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.00,0:21:47.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我也反省了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.48,0:21:49.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.94,0:21:53.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很中意現在的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.96,0:21:59.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.44,0:21:59.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.08,0:22:02.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯個蛋啊 橘子拿來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.03,0:22:04.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,橘子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.69,0:22:09.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶 我一直以來都很想問的 為什麼你喜歡橘子呀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.03,0:22:13.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我絕對不會告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.51,0:22:16.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼啊 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.25,0:22:18.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說不告訴你就是不告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.44,0:22:19.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊 小氣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.61,0:22:21.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說什麼 好痛痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.08,0:22:21.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你幹什麼啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.97,0:22:23.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如若您光臨本地
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.05,0:22:27.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,方便的話 請順便來冱木神社坐坐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.33,0:22:30.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你會遇到我那悠閒的宮司爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.90,0:22:37.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說不定還會遇見一位怕麻煩且有點毒舌的狐神大人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.56,0:24:15.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稻荷神社就是指供奉狐神大人的神社
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.77,0:24:19.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家的身邊 都有些什麼樣的稻荷神社啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.74,0:24:22.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集 彼此讓步
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.74,0:24:24.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,願神明保佑你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ED
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.34,0:22:44.78,OP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}遠く聞こえてる　人の声
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.88,0:22:51.24,OP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}振り返り　ほくそ笑む
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.74,0:22:55.49,OP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}一から百になる刹那Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.60,0:23:14.09,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}その一瞬が　永遠だね
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.32,0:23:15.01,OP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}孤独さえ支配したいと思ったけど
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.94,0:23:26.09,OP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}疑心暗鬼　敵わないや　手を伸ばそう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.90,0:23:38.25,OP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}世界の始まりは偽りの物語
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.66,0:23:45.15,OP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}月がそっと笑ってるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.20,0:23:50.76,OP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}なる歌の未来へと
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.86,0:23:55.45,OP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}繋ぐメッセージ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.51,0:24:08.17,OP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}僕を空へ導いてくれるSTORY
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.34,0:22:44.78,OP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}遠處傳來的 誰的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.88,0:22:51.24,OP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}回過頭去 暗自嬉笑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.74,0:22:55.49,OP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}從一到百那霎那瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.60,0:23:04.09,OP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}也將是永遠
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.32,0:23:15.01,OP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}原以為自己可以支配孤獨
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.94,0:23:26.09,OP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}但卻疑心暗鬼 果然敵不過 索性伸出雙手
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.90,0:23:38.25,OP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}世界的起始是個虛偽的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.66,0:23:45.15,OP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}月亮不禁一旁竊笑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.20,0:23:50.76,OP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}這或許是連接
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.86,0:23:55.45,OP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}那歡聲歌語未來的信息
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.51,0:24:08.17,OP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}指引我飛上天空的STORY

